headline: What Are They Hiding? Democrats Argue Voting Machines Too Fragile to Inspect – If Investigators Touch Them They WIll Need to Be Replaced – Demand Rudy Giuliani Be Punished for Requesting Access to Dominion Machines
author: Jim Hoft
sentences:
TRENDING: Swamp Rat Mitch McConnell Said He Was "Exhilarated" on Jan 6 that President Trump "Had Finally Tarnished His Reputation"

Also in Arizona election workers were caught on video deleting “archived” files before the machines were turned over to investigators.
Democrats and their media lackeys are so certain of this that they will not allow anyone to inspect the voting machines.
Democrats are ABSOLUTELY TERRIFIED that a reputable audit team may inspect the county’s Dominion voting machines.
How dare Rudy Giuliani or any Republican request an audit on such a fragile, sophisticated machine.
Democrats want you to know inspecting Dominion Voting Machines IS NOT ALLOWED!
Democrat and their media lackeys insist this is likely criminal activity.
The machines were so delicate that they can never be audited.

Isn’t it clear what the Democrats are doing?
Are Americans going to fall for this?
